<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Password Changed</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
      background-color: #ffffff;
    }
    .header {
      background-color: #10b2bf;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
      color: white;
    }
    .logo-container {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .main-logo {
      width: 120px;
      height: auto;
    }
    .name-logo {
      width: 180px;
      height: auto;
      margin-top: 10px;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 20px;
      background-color: #f9f9f9;
      border-radius: 4px;
    }
    .warning {
      color: #9a3b3b;
      font-style: italic;
    }
    .info-box {
      background-color: #e8f4f8;
      padding: 15px;
      border-radius: 4px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      border-left: 4px solid #10b2bf;
    }
    .footer {
      margin-top: 20px;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #777;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <div class="logo-container">
        <img src="https://makronexus.com/assets/md_logo_small2-CMnD-u5x.png" alt="Company Logo" class="main-logo">
        <br>
        <img src="https://makronexus.com/assets/md_logo_small4-Ci-XwfWu.png" alt="Company Name" class="name-logo">
      </div>
      <h1>Password Changed</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <p>Hello {{name}},</p>
      
      <p>We're confirming that your password for School Database System was successfully changed on <strong>{{timestamp}}</strong>.</p>
      
      <div class="info-box">
        <p>If you made this change, you don't need to take any further action.</p>
      </div>
      
      <p class="warning">If you didn't change your password, please contact our support team immediately or reset your password by visiting the login page and clicking on "Forgot Password".</p>
      
      <p>Best regards,<br>School Database System Security Team</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>&copy; {{year}} School Database System. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
